---
title: Cheesy Beef Meatballs & Tomato Sauce with Cauli-Potato Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: The trick to keeping these beef meatballs succulent and moist is a fabulous tomato sauce, and once you’ve mastered how
to perfectly balance the flavours in yours, you’ll never look back.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65a074941ee0609964a9c9e1-3cee1140.jpeg
